    "input_kind": "abstract_like",
    "source_label": "Demo abstract-like fixture",
    "source_text": "Abstract\nThis bounded reference abstract proposes a history semantics proto-module for conversation-like material. The raw text remains authoritative, while higher semantic artifacts are provenance-linked overlays.\n\nThe module separates chronology from inferential maturity and reconstructs O, E, and U lanes explicitly when the local material supports them. It aims to stabilize a bootstrap corpus around ODEU emergence and produce a workspace snapshot for later corpus waves.\n\nBecause the abstract does not specify detailed operator rules, the deontic lane remains underdetermined here.",
